[## [SECTION: Common Errors and Fixes — Phases 6 & 7]]


137
03:03:42,000 --> 03:03:48,000
Let me walk through common errors in Phases 6 and 7.
And how to fix them.

138
03:03:48,000 --> 03:03:54,000
Error one. permission denied on vault-bootstrap.sh.
The file is not executable.

139
03:03:54,000 --> 03:04:00,000
The fix is simple. Run chmod plus x on the script file.
Then try again.

140
03:04:00,000 --> 03:04:06,000
Error two. listener permission denied on port 8200.
Another process is already using that port.

141
03:04:06,000 --> 03:04:12,000
Run lsof dash i colon 8200 to find the process.
Then kill it and restart Vault.

142
03:04:12,000 --> 03:04:18,000
Error three. connection refused to Vault in CI.
Vault is only for Kubernetes, not for CI.

143
03:04:18,000 --> 03:04:24,000
CI should use environment variables from GitHub Secrets.
Not try to connect to a Vault instance.

144
03:04:24,000 --> 03:04:30,000
Error four. POSTGRES_PASSWORD required in unit tests.
Your settings validation requires the password.

145
03:04:30,000 --> 03:04:36,000
Set POSTGRES_PASSWORD in your CI environment variables.
Use a test password like test dash pg dash password.

146
03:04:36,000 --> 03:04:42,000
Error five. gitleaks fails on dot env example.
The placeholder values look like real secrets.

147
03:04:42,000 --> 03:04:48,000
The fix is to add these placeholders to the allowlist.
Update dot gitleaks.toml with the regexes.

148
03:04:48,000 --> 03:04:54,000
Error six. Trivy not finding the image.
The image hasn't been built locally.

149
03:04:54,000 --> 03:05:00,000
Run docker build first.
Then run trivy image against the local image name.

150
03:05:00,000 --> 03:05:06,000
Error seven. conftest command not found.
The tool isn't installed on your system.

151
03:05:06,000 --> 03:05:12,000
On macOS, run brew install conftest.
On Linux, download the binary from GitHub.

152
03:05:12,000 --> 03:05:18,000
Error eight. schema not found in CI.
The path to the SQL file is incorrect.

153
03:05:18,000 --> 03:05:24,000
Check your ci.yml file. Make sure the path matches.
Should be infrastructure slash docker slash init slash create_schema.sql.

154
03:05:24,000 --> 03:05:30,000
Error nine. dynamic credentials expire mid-request.
The TTL is too short or the renewal is missed.

155
03:05:30,000 --> 03:05:36,000
In production, Vault Agent handles renewal automatically.
Make sure the sidecar is running in your pod.

156
03:05:36,000 --> 03:05:42,000
Bookmark this section.
When you hit an error, you'll know exactly where to look.


